    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable new ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-cared for and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for those daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. It\u2019s super dependable and just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see how great it feels on the road! \u2728",
