    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This S54-powered legend offers a visceral, naturally aspirated experience. Featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, the engine pulls cleanly through the rev range. Significant preventative maintenance is addressed, including Double VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed manual transmission shifts with tactile precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Equipped with an upgraded suspension setup for enhanced lateral grip and communicative steering, this chassis remains composed under load. A mechanically robust example for the discerning driver.",
