    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor road wear consistent with careful ownership and garage storage. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is supple and free of significant wear, and every electronic feature\u2014from the climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready, having undergone regular fluid changes and preventative maintenance to ensure a smooth, responsive drive. It has been smoke-free and treated with genuine care, preserving a premium feel that is evident the moment you step inside. This is a reliable, high-performing vehicle for a buyer who values a well-documented service history and aesthetic pride.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
