    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it runs like a dream and looks great too. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable vehicle that won't let you down, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'd love to chat!",
