    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. This example delivers linear power through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is excellent, with the rear subframe reinforcement already completed for long-term durability. The suspension features refreshed bushings and uprated dampers, maintaining the precise kinematics of the original MacPherson strut/multi-link design. Documented maintenance includes recent valve lash adjustments and Rod Bearing service, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain remains within factory tolerances. A true driver\u2019s machine with exceptional analog feedback and peak atmospheric performance.",
